title: Ep - 176 - TAREK EL MOUSSA FROM HGTV’S FLIP OR FLOP
description:
Tarek El Moussa is a real estate investor and co- star of HGTV’s show Flip or Flop. Kate asks Tarek about how he began his career in real estate, how he landed a show on HGTV, his health issues, and what it is like to film with his ex-wife. 


Film Director and Producer John Ward reviews this week’s episode of Southern Charm on Bravo. 


Lifestyle blogger Danielle Schaffer reviews Kate Plus Date on TLC.
